headline: Q4 Rundown: Aflac (NYSE:AFL) Vs Other Life Insurance Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Aflac (NYSE:AFL) and the rest of the life insurance stocks fared in Q4.

headline: Is It Time To Reassess Aflac (AFL) After Its Recent Share Price Weakness?
summary: If you are wondering whether Aflac at around US$112 a share represents fair value or a stretched price, this article walks through what that number could mean for you. The stock has had mixed recent returns, with a 2.6% decline over the last 7 days, a 5.0% return across 30 days, 2.0% year to date, and 7.7% over 1 year. The 3-year return is very large, and the 5-year return is around 1.6x. Recent coverage of Aflac has focused on it as a large, established insurance name that investors often...
